authors: A Name Not Yet Taken AB
description:
Stemmers for 12 languages and one default stemmer.  The default stemmer (DefaultStemmer) can be used for languages that not are supported. The default stemmer does not do any stemming at all.

Supported languages
Danish
Dutch
English
Finnish
French
German
Italian
Norwegian
Portuguese
Romanian
Spanish
Swedish
releaseNotes:
This version includes stemmers for 10 more languages and every stemmer in this version has been tested in extensive tests with more than 20000 words in each test.

New stemmers
Danish
Dutch
Finnish
French
German
Italian
Norwegian
